  "title": "Sales and Marketing Executive (Training provide & Career progression)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></h2><h3><strong>Start Your Career in Sales & Marketing – Grow with a Team That Supports You</strong></h3><p>We are expanding our team and looking for Sales & Marketing Executive to support our brand growth through events, campaigns, and on ground marketing activities. <br /></p><p>This roles is ideal for individuals who enjoy people interaction, creative marketing, and brand representation. You will work closely with the team to execute campaigns, engage audience, and build strong brand presence across multiple channels.<br /></p><h3><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h3><p><p>A positive, driven attitude and a willingness to learn<br />Strong communication skills and leadership potential<br />A team player who enjoys working with people and building connections<br />Fresh graduates and candidates with relevant experience are welcome. </p></p><h3><strong>What You’ll Gain</strong></h3><ul><li><p>1-on-1 mentorship and full training provided</p></li><li><p>A clear path for career growth and leadership opportunities</p></li><li><p>A supportive, energetic, and collaborative team culture</p></li><li><p>Travel opportunities—locally and internationally</p></li><li><p>Recognition and rewards for your performance and contributions</p></li></ul><p>If you're looking for more than just a job—and want a place where you can grow, learn, and be part of something exciting—this could be the perfect opportunity for you.</p><p><strong>Apply now and send us your resume.</strong><br /><strong>We’re excited to hear from you.</strong></p><p><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</em></p>",
